I"”<h1 id="clipboard">Clipboard</h1>

<div class="infobox box text-center">
    <p style="text-align:center;"><img src="../../assets/images/icons/minecolonies/clipboard.png" alt="Clipboard" /></p>
    <recipe>clipboard</recipe>
</div>

<p>The clipboard is an easy way to see all the requests your workers have (that are not being fulfilled by a <a href="../../source/workers/courier">Courier</a>).</p>

<h2 id="using-the-clipboard">Using the Clipboard</h2>

<p>When you first make the clipboard and right-click anywhere, you will get a message to sneak + right-click on the <a href="../../source/buildings/townhall">Town Hall</a> to register the clipboard.</p>

<p><br /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><img src="../../assets/images/misc/clipboardinitmessage.png" alt="Clipboard Initial Message" /></p>
<p><br /></p>

<p>After you register the clipboard, this message will appear:
<br /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><img src="../../assets/images/misc/clipboardregistered.png" alt="Clipboard Registered Message" /></p>
<p><br /></p>

<p>Now when you right-click while holding the clipboard, you will see all your citizensâ€™ requests on the clipboard (that are not being fulfilled by a <a href="../../source/workers/courier">Courier</a>)!</p>

<p><br /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><img src="../../assets/images/gui/clipboardgui1.png" alt="Clipboard GUI" /></p>
<p><br /></p>

<p>If you click on the exclamation mark in the top right, you will only see requests for things that workers need <em>right now.</em></p>

<p><br /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><img src="../../assets/images/gui/clipboardgui2.png" alt="Clipboard GUI Important Requests" /></p>
<p><br /></p>
